ink 1-min.jpg\" alt=\"Starlink and internet installation showcase\" class=\"h-64 w-full object-cover transition duration-500 group-hover:scale-105\"/><div class=\"p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900\">Starlink &amp; Internet Setup</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-slate-600 text-sm\">Fast Starlink alignment and router configuration for reliable connectivity.</p></div></a></div></section><section class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto -mt-10 px-6 relative z-10\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-200\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg text-slate-900 mb-2\">Affordable Pricing</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Top-quality products and services starting from Kes 1,500.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-200\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg text-slate-900 mb-2\">Flexible &amp; Fast</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Enjoy same-day installations and extended working hours to fit your schedule.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-200\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg text-slate-900 mb-2\">Premium Quality</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Accredited installers using genuine products with an included warranty.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto py-20 px-6 bg-slate-100 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 shadow-xl\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Our Professional Installation Services</h2><p class=\"text-slate-600 mt-2\">Accredited and expert solutions across Kenya</p></div><div id=\"services\" class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-slate-200 flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow\"><div><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-snug\">Satellite TV Installation</h3></div><p class=\"text-slate-600 text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Accredited installation and setup for Dstv, Zuku, Startimes, Gotv, and Azam. Enjoy clear signal and expert support.</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-6\"><li class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400\"></span>Dish &amp; decoder setup</li><li class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400\"></span>Xtraview &amp; extra TV points</li><li class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400\"></span>Signal repair &amp; realignment</li></ul></div><div class=\"border-t border-slate-200 pt-4 flex justify-between items-center\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider\">From</span><span class=\"text-lg font-black text-blue-600\">Kes 1,500</span></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-slate-200 flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow\"><div><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-snug\">TV Wall Mounting</h3></div><p class=\"text-slate-600 text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Professional mounting for all TV sizes with tilt, swivel, or ceiling brackets. Clean finish and secure installation.</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-6\"><li class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400\"></span>Swivel &amp; tilt brackets</li><li class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400\"></span>Cable management</li><li class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400\"></span>Sound bar &amp; home theater setup</li></ul></div><div class=\"border-t border-slate-200 pt-4 flex justify-between items-center\"><spa